I've gone through the full Blue Nile necklace catalog for {{month_year}}. Every solitaire pendant. Every tennis necklace. Every James Allen design that migrated over after the brand shutdown. Real prices, real affiliate links — Blue Nile pays this site a commission if you buy, which doesn't change my opinions.

